### Get all books
GET http://localhost:3000/books

### Add new book
POST http://localhost:3000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Wings of Fire",
  "author": "Abdul Kalam"
}

### Update book by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title"
}

### Delete book by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/books/3
